                Templum <lb n="2"/>Deii <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>Sol</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Inv</abbr><ex>icti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Mit</abbr><ex>hrae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Aure<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan></supplied> Iusti<lb break="no" n="4"/>nianus <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimus</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>dux labefa<lb break="no" n="6"/>ctatum re<lb break="no" n="7"/>stituit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: Fitz: vermutlich vor dem 27. Juni 310, als Aurelius Senecio das Amt des dux von Pannonia Prima und Noricum Ripense antrat. (B): Selem: Z. 1/2: Zeilenfall nicht angegeben; Z. 2: dei.</p>
            </div>
